---
import MainLayout from '../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';

const title = "高雄術後居家照護｜出院後照顧服務";
const description = "專業術後居家照護，協助傷口觀察與清潔照護、用藥提醒、復健協助，幫助患者安心休養，安心在家休養。";
const canonicalURL = new URL("/services/post-surgery/", Astro.site);
---

<MainLayout title={title} description={description} canonicalURL={canonicalURL}>
  <script type="application/ld+json" slot="head">
    {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "Service",
      "name": "高雄術後居家照護",
      "description": "手術後返家照護，協助傷口觀察與清潔照護、用藥提醒、復健協助，幫助患者安心休養",
      "provider": {"@type": "Organization", "name": "宇涵居家照護"},
      "areaServed": {"@type": "City", "name": "高雄市"},
      "serviceType": "術後照顧",
      "url": "https://yuhanhomecare.com/services/post-surgery/"
    }
  </script>

  <section class="relative bg-[#fcfaf6] overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-1/2 h-full bg-[#efe5d5] opacity-30 rounded-bl-[100px]"></div>
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 lg:py-24 relative">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <nav aria-label="breadcrumb" class="mb-4">
          <ol class="flex text-sm text-[#6d5d50]">
            <li><a href="/" class="hover:text-[#8b621f] transition-colors">首頁</a></li>
            <li class="mx-2">/</li>
            <li><a href="/services/" class="hover:text-[#8b621f] transition-colors">服務項目</a></li>
            <li class="mx-2">/</li>
            <li class="text-[#2b221c] font-medium" aria-current="page">術後照顧</li>
          </ol>
        </nav>
        <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-[#2b221c] mb-4 leading-tight">高雄術後居家照護</h1>
        <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-[#6d5d50] leading-relaxed">專業術後照護，陪伴您順利度過恢復期的每一天</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 lg:py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
        <div class="lg:col-span-2">
          <img src="/images/blog-postsurgery.jpg" alt="高雄術後居家照護服務" class="w-full h-80 object-cover rounded-2xl mb-10 shadow-md" loading="lazy" width="800" height="320" />

          <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-[#2b221c] mb-6">術後照護的重要性</h2>
          <p class="text-[#6d5d50] leading-relaxed mb-6">手術後的恢復期是整個治療過程中極為關鍵的階段。患者在經歷手術後，身體處於虛弱狀態，可能面臨傷口疼痛、行動不便、飲食限制、用藥管理等多方面的挑戰。這個時期如果沒有得到適當的照顧，不僅可能影響傷口癒合速度，甚至可能造成併發症，延長恢復時間或影響手術效果。</p>
          <p class="text-[#6d5d50] leading-relaxed mb-6">許多患者與家屬在面臨出院時會感到擔憂與不安。醫院的照護資源充足，但回到家中後，誰來幫忙傷口敷料更換（依醫囑）？誰來確認用藥時間？誰來協助上下床與如廁？這些問題讓許多出院患者家庭倍感壓力。宇涵的術後居家照護服務正是為了解決這個問題而存在——我們將專業的術後照護延伸到患者的家中，讓患者可以在熟悉的環境中安心休養。</p>
          <p class="text-[#6d5d50] leading-relaxed mb-6">術後照護的目標不僅僅是照顧患者的日常生活，更重要的是協助患者安心休養、盡早恢復自理能力。專業的術後看護能夠正確執行醫療指示，觀察恢復進度，及時發現異常狀況，並給予患者與家屬正確的衛教指導。這些都是一般家庭成員難以做到的專業照護。</p>
          <p class="text-[#6d5d50] leading-relaxed mb-10">宇涵的術後照護團隊具備豐富的臨床經驗，熟悉各種手術後的照護要點。無論是骨科手術、心臟手術、腹腔手術、癌症手術、眼科手術或整形外科手術，我們都能提供專業的術後照護服務。我們的看護人員會密切配合醫療團隊的指示，確保患者術後恢復順利。</p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-[#2b221c] mb-6">常見術後照護類型</h2>
          <p class="text-[#6d5d50] leading-relaxed mb-6">宇涵的術後照護服務涵蓋多種手術類型，以下是常見的術後照護需求：</p>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-10">
            <div class="border border-[#efe5d5] rounded-xl p-5 hover:border-[#8b621f] transition-colors"><h3 class="font-bold text-[#2b221c] mb-2">骨科手術後照護</h3><p class="text-sm text-[#6d5d50]">人工關節置換、骨折固定、脊椎手術等，協助復健運動、行動輔助、疼痛管理。</p></div>
            <div class="border border-[#efe5d5] rounded-xl p-5 hover:border-[#8b621f] transition-colors"><h3 class="font-bold text-[#2b221c] mb-2">心臟手術後照護</h3><p class="text-sm text-[#6d5d50]">心導管手術、心臟繞道手術、心律調節器裝置等，監測生命徵象、注意活動限制。</p></div>
            <div class="border border-[#efe5d5] rounded-xl p-5 hover:border-[#8b621f] transition-colors"><h3 class="font-bold text-[#2b221c] mb-2">癌症手術後照護</h3><p class="text-sm text-[#6d5d50]">腫瘤切除、器官部分切除等，傷口觀察與清潔照護、營養支持、情緒支持、副作用觀察。</p></div>
            <div class="border border-[#efe5d5] rounded-xl p-5 hover:border-[#8b621f] transition-colors"><h3 class="font-bold text-[#2b221c] mb-2">腹腔手術後照護</h3><p class="text-sm text-[#6d5d50]">膽囊切除、闌尾切除、腸胃手術等，飲食調整、傷口觀察、活動指導。</p></div>
            <div class="border border-[#efe5d5] rounded-xl p-5 hover:border-[#8b621f] transition-colors"><h3 class="font-bold text-[#2b221c] mb-2">婦科/泌尿科手術</h3><p class="text-sm text-[#6d5d50]">子宮切除、攝護腺手術等，術後休養、傷口觀察與清潔照護、日常生活協助。</p></div>
            <div class="border border-[#efe5d5] rounded-xl p-5 hover:border-[#8b621f] transition-colors"><h3 class="font-bold text-[#2b221c] mb-2">眼科/整形手術</h3><p class="text-sm text-[#6d5d50]">白內障手術、眼部整形等，術後姿勢維持、用藥協助、日常活動限制提醒。</p></div>
          </div>

          <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-[#2b221c] mb-6">術後照護服務內容</h2>
          <div class="space-y-6 mb-10">
            <div class="bg-[#fcfaf6] p-6 rounded-xl"><div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3"><div class="w-10 h-10 bg-[#8b621f] bg-opacity-10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#8b621f]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg></div><h3 class="font-bold text-[#2b221c]">傷口觀察與清潔照護觀察</h3></div><p class="text-sm text-[#6d5d50] leading-relaxed">觀察手術傷口的癒合狀況，注意紅腫、熱痛、滲液等異常徵兆，協助傷口敷料更換（依醫囑）與保持傷口清潔乾燥，並記錄傷口變化回報家屬與醫療團隊。</p></div>
            <div class="bg-[#fcfaf6] p-6 rounded-xl"><div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3"><div class="w-10 h-10 bg-[#8b621f] bg-opacity-10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#8b621f]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg></div><h3 class="font-bold text-[#2b221c]">用藥提醒與管理</h3></div><p class="text-sm text-[#6d5d50] leading-relaxed">依照醫囑時間提醒病患準時服用藥物，記錄用藥情形，觀察有無藥物副作用或不適反應，並於回診時提供用藥紀錄給醫師參考。</p></div>
            <div class="bg-[#fcfaf6] p-6 rounded-xl"><div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3"><div class="w-10 h-10 bg-[#8b621f] bg-opacity-10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#8b621f]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"></path></svg></div><h3 class="font-bold text-[#2b221c]">生活起居全面協助</h3></div><p class="text-sm text-[#6d5d50] leading-relaxed">協助病患上下床、盥洗、如廁、更衣等日常活動，避免因行動不便導致跌倒或其他意外。</p></div>
            <div class="bg-[#fcfaf6] p-6 rounded-xl"><div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3"><div class="w-10 h-10 bg-[#8b621f] bg-opacity-10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#8b621f]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path></svg></div><h3 class="font-bold text-[#2b221c]">復健運動協助</h3></div><p class="text-sm text-[#6d5d50] leading-relaxed">依照醫師或物理治療師指示，協助病患進行居家復健運動，包括主動運動、被動關節活動、行走訓練等。</p></div>
            <div class="bg-[#fcfaf6] p-6 rounded-xl"><div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3"><div class="w-10 h-10 bg-[#8b621f] bg-opacity-10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#8b621f]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M3 3h2l.4 2M7 13h10l4-8H5.4M7 13L5.4 5M7 13l-2.293 2.293c-.63.63-.184 1.707.707 1.707H17m0 0a2 2 0 100 4 2 2 0 000-4zm-8 2a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path></svg></div><h3 class="font-bold text-[#2b221c]">營養飲食準備</h3></div><p class="text-sm text-[#6d5d50] leading-relaxed">依照醫師建議的飲食原則，準備適合術後恢復的營養餐點，注意飲食禁忌與營養均衡。</p></div>
            <div class="bg-[#fcfaf6] p-6 rounded-xl"><div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3"><div class="w-10 h-10 bg-[#8b621f] bg-opacity-10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#8b621f]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"></path></svg></div><h3 class="font-bold text-[#2b221c]">回診陪同</h3></div><p class="text-sm text-[#6d5d50] leading-relaxed">陪伴病患返回醫院回診、拆線、檢查，協助記錄醫師指示與後續照護注意事項。</p></div>
          </div>

          <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-[#2b221c] mb-6">術後照護注意事項</h2>
          <p class="text-[#6d5d50] leading-relaxed mb-6">術後恢復期有許多需要注意的事項，宇涵的看護人員會特別留意以下幾點，並指導家屬正確的照護方式：</p>
          <ul class="space-y-3 mb-10">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#8b621f] flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg><span class="text-[#6d5d50]"><strong class="text-[#2b221c]">傷口感染徵兆：</strong>觀察傷口是否有紅腫、發熱、疼痛加劇、膿性分泌物或異味，體溫是否升高。</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#8b621f] flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg><span class="text-[#6d5d50]"><strong class="text-[#2b221c]">活動限制遵守：</strong>依照醫師指示限制活動範圍與強度，避免過度活動影響傷口癒合或造成二次傷害。</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#8b621f] flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg><span class="text-[#6d5d50]"><strong class="text-[#2b221c]">飲食原則：</strong>注意術後飲食禁忌，確保營養充足且易於消化，促進傷口癒合與體力恢復。</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#8b621f] flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg><span class="text-[#6d5d50]"><strong class="text-[#2b221c]">按時用藥：</strong>確保止痛藥、抗生素等藥物按時服用，不隨意增減劑量或停藥。</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#8b621f] flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg><span class="text-[#6d5d50]"><strong class="text-[#2b221c]">預防跌倒：</strong>術後患者因麻醉藥物、體力虛弱、行動受限等原因容易跌倒，需特別注意環境安全。</span></li>
          </ul>

          <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-[#2b221c] mb-6">費用參考</h2>
          <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-6">
            <table class="w-full text-left border-collapse">
              <thead><tr class="bg-[#2b221c] text-[#fcfaf6]"><th class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold">服務方案</th><th class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold">說明</th><th class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold">參考費用</th></tr></thead>
              <tbody class="divide-y divide-[#efe5d5]">
                <tr class="hover:bg-[#fcfaf6]"><td class="px-6 py-4 text-[#2b221c]">短期術後照護</td><td class="px-6 py-4 text-[#6d5d50]">1-2週，12小時/日</td><td class="px-6 py-4 text-[#8b621f] font-semibold">$2,200 - $2,500 /日</td></tr>
                <tr class="hover:bg-[#fcfaf6]"><td class="px-6 py-4 text-[#2b221c]">中期術後照護</td><td class="px-6 py-4 text-[#6d5d50]">2-4週，12小時/日</td><td class="px-6 py-4 text-[#8b621f] font-semibold">$2,100 - $2,400 /日</td></tr>
                <tr class="hover:bg-[#fcfaf6]"><td class="px-6 py-4 text-[#2b221c]">24小時術後照護</td><td class="px-6 py-4 text-[#6d5d50]">全天候照護</td><td class="px-6 py-4 text-[#8b621f] font-semibold">$2,500 - $2,900 /日</td></tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#6d5d50]">* 中長期照護另有優惠。實際費用依手術類型與照護需求評估。</p>
        </div>

        <aside class="lg:col-span-1">
          <div class="bg-[#fcfaf6] rounded-2xl p-6 sticky top-8">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#2b221c] mb-4">其他服務項目</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8">
              <li><a href="/services/home-care/" class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[#6d5d50] hover:text-[#8b621f] transition-colors"><span class="text-[#8b621f]">→</span> 居家看護</a></li>
              <li><a href="/services/hospital-care/" class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[#6d5d50] hover:text-[#8b621f] transition-colors"><span class="text-[#8b621f]">→</span> 醫院看護</a></li>
              <li><a href="/services/elderly-care/" class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[#6d5d50] hover:text-[#8b621f] transition-colors"><span class="text-[#8b621f]">→</span> 長者陪伴</a></li>
              <li><a href="/services/dementia-care/" class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[#6d5d50] hover:text-[#8b621f] transition-colors"><span class="text-[#8b621f]">→</span> 失智照護</a></li>
              <li><a href="/services/temporary-care/" class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[#6d5d50] hover:text-[#8b621f] transition-colors"><span class="text-[#8b621f]">→</span> 臨時看護</a></li>
            </ul>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#2b221c] mb-4">快速聯絡</h3>
            <a href="tel:0935803258" class="block w-full text-center bg-[#8b621f] text-white py-4 rounded-full font-semibold hover:bg-[#6d4a18] transition-colors mb-3"><span class="text-sm block opacity-80">24小時服務專線</span><span class="text-lg">0935-803-258</span></a>
            <a href="/contact/" class="block w-full text-center border-2 border-[#8b621f] text-[#8b621f] py-3 rounded-full font-semibold hover:bg-[#8b621f] hover:text-white transition-colors">線上諮詢表單</a>
          </div>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 lg:py-20 bg-[#2b221c]">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-[#fcfaf6] mb-4">術後照護，交給宇涵安心</h2>
      <p class="text-[#efe5d5] mb-8 leading-relaxed">讓專業看護陪伴您度過術後恢復期，順利重返健康生活。</p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="tel:0935803258" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-[#8b621f] text-white rounded-full font-semibold text-lg hover:bg-[#6d4a18] transition-colors shadow-lg">撥打 0935-803-258</a>
        <a href="/contact/" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 border-2 border-[#efe5d5] text-[#fcfaf6] rounded-full font-semibold hover:bg-[#efe5d5] hover:text-[#2b221c] transition-colors">填寫諮詢表單</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
